        "answer_count": 2,
        "title": "How to create a Spring Boot test that runs with specific JVM arguments",
        "body": "<p>I want a to create a test for my spring boot application that uses specific JVM arguments, I want the JVM arguments to be used with only this test.<\/p>\n\n<p>Is this possible ? My goal is to set up a proxy for just one test, so if there is another approach to achieve that, please suggest it.<\/p>\n",
