            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 4.0",
            "score": 12,
            "is_accepted": true,
            "last_activity_date": 1584016575,
            "creation_date": 1584016575,
            "body": "<p>I solved this by adding a static bloc in the class and setting the system properties:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>static {\n    System.setProperty(\"http.proxyHost\", \"myproxyserver.com\");\n    System.setProperty(\"http.proxyPort\", \"80\");\n    System.setProperty(\"https.proxyHost\", \"myproxyserver.com\");\n    System.setProperty(\"https.proxyPort\", \"80\");\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
            "answer_id": 60654275,
            "question_id": 60637867
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://i.sstatic.net/h8aNr.jpg?s=256",
                "account_id": 4440595,
                "user_type": "registered",
                "user_id": 3615207,
                "link": "https://stackoverflow.com/users/3615207/stinger",
                "reputation": 4265,
                "display_name": "stinger",
                "accept_rate": 73
            },
            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 4.0",
            "score": 1,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1583962275,
            "creation_date": 1583936152,
            "body": "<p>If you're using IntelliJ Idea, you can pass arguments to test from Run/Debug configuration -> VM options.\nIf you're using Maven, you can pass arguments in surefire-plugin configuration:<\/p>\n\n<pre class=\"lang-xml prettyprint-override\"><code>        &lt;plugin&gt;\n            &lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&lt;/groupId&gt;\n            &lt;artifactId&gt;maven-surefire-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n            &lt;configuration&gt;\n                &lt;argLine&gt;-Xmx1G&lt;/argLine&gt;\n            &lt;/configuration&gt;\n        &lt;/plugin&gt;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>And remember, that Maven options overrides Idea defaults (if set).<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 60638118,
            "question_id": 60637867,
            "last_edit_date": 1583962275
        }
    ],
